Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,友军?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:56.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\fs35\frz18.27\pos(777,434)}孤身二人的谋反者们
